# Proto generated stubs are CHECKED IN (by design — see proto/README.md).
# Week 2 switched to `buf generate`; the committed stubs guarantee that
# `go build` and `pytest` don't require buf to be installed. CI still
# re-runs `buf generate` and diffs the result to catch drift.
